body_html:
I think there might be more wrong. Installed the build to check on gmm_test.py ... the test worked BUT there was a error message about cuinit and some of my test apps don't find a gpu.
Don't know why the unittests are not failing on mass.
The build break came with a large merge ... maybe something else came in. Going to take a look first thing tomorrow.
